{
  "stem": "24554.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A very interesting thing was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When I work, there were forced labor people, I work with a Tajik-- you know, I was thinking, he's a Tajik.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What happens?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We started to talking, I come from Europe, I am a Jewish, yes?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he tell me, you know, I am a Jewish, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this-- what happens to you, and all of Europe people, it was a punishment from God, why you run away from the religion.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I say, how you can talk like that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I am a Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am from one from the 12 Jewish this-- very religious, no different religious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not like the-- like the Jewish from Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said it was a punishment from God-- that Hitler was a punishment to the Jewish from God.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked there [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 19-- end of-- beginning 1942, or so.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How old were you at this point, Albert?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, around 28, so you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So started, you know, the government, the [INAUDIBLE] government in London, you know, started making agreement with the Soviets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the Soviets accept the existence of Czechoslovakia, occupied by Germany-- but the government was in London.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this time, I heard, they start Czechoslovak army, you know, in Russia-- they give permission to-- before us was the Polish army, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Sikorsky [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they started this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I go to the police, you know, the interior.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will go to the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You are not a Czechoslovak, you are a stateless Jewish-- this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, yes, I heard it in the radio, or somewhere somebody told us from this, they exist, and I am entitled to go.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
